guide: 7Carrots and potatoes from killing
7Zombies in graveyard do count.
7Use /warp trapper to accept a quest
7and use SkyHanni's Trapper features
7to make this easier. Bring a bow with you.
7Mine Diamonds in the Mines of Divan
7(HotM 3) or in the carts in the Dwarven Mines.
7You can also passively work on this by using
7Diamond Spreadings in your Minions if you want.
7Wear armor enchanted with Growth 5
7(Enchanting Level 5).
7Applying Growth 5 costs 50 Levels each.
7Kill t2 Revenant Horrors to passively
7progress in the Community Goal.
7Optimal tool:
7Golden Axe with Efficiency 5
7Reforges: Double-Bit or Lush
7Get Haste 3 from a splash to instamine wood
7Forage in The Park to get wood for your minions.
7Place as many minions as you can
7give them a medium storage and the best fuel
7you can. Collect them in time.
7You will gain progress here passively
7while going for other grinds.
7lMake sure to always have a pet active!
7Use a Silk Touch and Efficiency Golden Axe and
7chop mushroom blocks in the Mushroom Desert.
7Optimal tool:
7Golden Axe with Efficiency 5
7Reforges: Double-Bit or Lush
7Get Haste 3 from a splash to instamine wood
7Costs 256 Enchanted Oak Wood to craft and
7unlocks at Oak Wood Collection 9 (30k).
7Get Enchanting Level 10 and play
7the highest experiments in the
7Experimentation Table that you can get.
7Kill endermen and mine Nodes for
7Enchanted Ender Pearls. You need them for
7Enchanted Eyes of Ender (32 of those).
7Don't forget to buy your daily Blaze Powder
7from the Alchemist in the Hub.

21.description: 7Equip an Uncommon or higher tiered Rock Pet
guide: 7You get the Rock Pet from mining ores.
7The Common Rock unlocks at 2.5k broken ores,
7the Uncommon one at 7.5k. You can also upgrade
7your common rock at Kat but this will take a day.
7Farm in the Garden. Remember Crop Milestones
7grant a lot of XP. Carrots can also benefit this
7as you can use pet candies made out of them to
7contribute to another goal.
7Fish in The Park and make sure rain is active.
7Do not stand/have your bobber under solid blocks
7as this will slow your speed down by a lot.
7You will get this passively by leveling up
7skills, if you don't forget to put the money
7in your bank ;-)
7Craft some easy minions while also getting
7those that will help with this Bingo.
7You might wanna go further than that to
7help with other goals.
7Craft Leather, Iron, Gold and Diamond Armor
7Collect Ender Armor from The End (8 pieces including equipment)
7Craft Leaflet, Farm Suit, Mushroom and Cactus Armor
7Buy Squire, Rosetta's, Celeste and Starlight Armor from Rosetta
7You will unlock this while going
7for Mushroom Collector.
7Remember to get the Glowstone Dust
7by buying a Glowstone from The Builder
7and breaking it on your island.
7Going for the Slayer Goal will give you
7quite some progress here if you do it
7on your own with Revenant Bosses.
7Reforge your Void Sword to Sharp
7at the Blacksmith in the Hub (-28 69 -125),
7or enchant any weapon with Critical 5 (costs 50 Levels).
7You might also get it from receiving a Splash.
7Kill Cows in The Barn to unlock this
7and craft it using the materials you
7got along the way.
7Follow the Lone Adventurers quest in The End
7until you get the Bow.
7Apply it to an armor piece using the Blacksmith.
7This can take quite some time and money
7as it is RNG based.
7To help with this, try to make bigger crafts
7by hand for Carpentry levels. Don't forget
7to do some Alchemy with Materials gathered from the Garden.
7Also do your daily experiments and make sure
7to have a pet active at all times
7(any pet works, even level 100).
7Do your daily commissions in the Dwarven Mines
7(and Crystal Hollows). Also participate in any
7active event there that you come across.
7Collect Superboom TNT from dungeons
7or buy some from Ophelia in The Dungeon Hub.
7Then use them on the crypts you run
7across inside a dungeon.

3.description: 7Obtain a Bronze Medal in a Farming Contest
guide: 7You need Farming Level 10 for this.
7Your best options will most likely be
7potato contests as you need a lot of
7potatoes for a different goal or mushroom
7contests with a silk touch gold axe.
7Open chests in the Crystal Hollows (Heart of the Mountain III),
7do commissions in The Dwarven Mines,
7claim your daily powder from the Puzzler and
7from giving Fetchur the items he asks for.
7Fetchurs items are all listed in the Wiki.
7Try to do those while a '2x Powder' event is active.
7Buy a Dirt Bottle (100k) from the
7Smithmonger in the Hub and reforge
7an uncommon or higher rarity weapon with it.
7You will most likely get this from
7leveling up skills.
7If that isnt enough, kill Endermen and
7mine nodes in The End to get money.
7Remember to actually put the money
7you get in the Bank :)
7Collect those you run along while doing other goals.
7If you have trouble check TimeDeo's fairy soul
7 tutorial on YouTube or use /neusouls on/off
7to get waypoints.
7Kill the Goblins you can find in the
7Dwarven Mines and Crystal Hollows.
7You will need Mining 12 for this.
7This requires Catacombs Level 3 and
7a completion of the 2 floors before.
7You may need help from party finder
7or friends for this.
7You will get this passively while going
7for other grinds as you need Combat 15 for
7the dungeon task. Dont forget to claim
7your bestiary rewards as you unlock them.
7Talk to Jamie in the Hub and
7claim the Rogue Sword from him.
7Right click it to gain +100 Speed.
7Or just wait for a splash.
7Kill Spiders in the Spider's Den (/warp spider)
7place a few Spider Minions and participate
7in killing Arachne in Arachne's Sanctuary.
7Recommended to wear a Cow Head to avoid the poison.
7Dont forget to fuel your minions and give them
7a storage. Also collect them in time.
7You need a score of 230 or higher
7in Floor 1 or higher to get this.
7Opening will cost 100k coins.
7You will most likely gain passive
7progress in here. Use the best pickaxe
7you can get your hands on and mine.
7Craft Leather, Iron, Gold and Diamond Armor
7Collect Ender Armor from The End (8 pieces including equipment)
7Craft Leaflet, Farm Suit, Mushroom and Cactus Armor
7Buy Squire, Rosetta's, Celeste and Starlight Armor from Rosetta
7Obtained from completing any race with 4/4
7at Guildford in the Dungeon Hub.

7Guardian, Bee, Dolphin, Reindeer, Rock, Tarantula,
7Owl and Zoo.
7lEggs:
7Jerry, Silverfish, Pig, Rabbit, Endermite and Bat.
7If you use eggs, you will need 2.5k Raw Chicken Collection

7Use the best rod you can get
7your hands on (Chum Rod is a good option),
7enchant it and don't forget to use baits.
7You might also want to use Angler Armor.
7Do 3 Tier 1 Revenant Horror Bosses

7Doing this will bring you decently close
7to your 10th Minion Slot which will be
7useful for other goals. Craft all the
7Minions you get across. Remember that
7you can buy material from a few NPCs.

7and equip them all in one lobby.
7You will get decent progress towards this
7while going for other grinds. You will most
7likely have to kill some Enderman in The End
7to finish this. Don't forget to claim your
7bestiary rewards.
7Kill Cows in The Barn to unlock this
7and craft it using the materials you
7got along the way.
7Carrots and potatoes from killing
7Zombies in graveyard do count.
7This requires Catacombs Level 1 and
7a completion of the previous floor.
7You may need help from party finder
7or friends for this.
7You can unlock 17/17 Farming Collections,
76/11 Combat Collections, 6/6 Foraging Collections,
714/22 Mining Collections for a total of 43 collections.
7You will also get some Fishing Collections.
7You will need Heart of the Mountain 3
7for this (this can be done by doing
74 commissions a day for 3 days). In the
7Crystal Hollows you will need to find
7Mines of Divan and 4 different tools in there.
7You will need Heart of the Mountain 3
7for this (this can be done by doing
74 commissions a day for 3 days). Aim to

7access to. Collect in time!
7Get yourself a splash, equip a Bingo Pet
7and get the cake buff by eating the cakes
7on owocato's, xMeru's or prtl's island.
7If this doesn't finish it, get a Void Sword (200k) in the End

7You might want to go for Sugar Cane
7in your Garden, but you can also use
7the wheat in The Hub.
7Talk to Jamie in the Hub and
7claim the Rogue Sword from him.
7Right click it to gain +100 Speed.
7Or just wait for a splash.
7Get Enchanting Level 10 and play
7the first tier in the Experimentation Table.

7Buy all 6 Talismans for 26k from the Adventurer in The Hub
7Collection Talismans:

7claim your daily powder from the Puzzler and
7from giving Fetchur the items he asks for.

7Try to do those while a '2x Powder' event is active.
7You will most likely get this from

7Cobblestone Generator on your island.

7Wear armor enchanted with Growth 5

7Get Haste 3 from a splash to instamine wood

7give them a medium storage and the best fuel
7you can. Collect them in time.

7Also do your daily experiments and make sure
7to have a pet active at all times
7(any pet works, even level 100).
7Ideally you'd want Ender Set
7with a Void Sword for this.
7Craft Leather, Iron, Gold and Diamond Armor
7Collect Ender Armor from The End (8 pieces)
7Craft Leaflet, Farm Suit, Mushroom and Cactus Armor.
7Brew a potion with an Enchanted Sugar Cane/
7Enchanted Gold (Block)/Enchanted Sugar (Cane)
7and add Glowstone to it. You can get that Glowstone
7by buying one block from the Builder and
7breaking it on your island.
7Kill Skeletons in The Deep Caverns
7to unlock Skeleton Minions. Craft as many
7as you can and place them on your island.
7Give them the best fuel and storage
7that you have access to and collect in time.
7Don't forget to buy your daily bones from
7The Adventurer in The Hub.
7Mine Diamonds in the Deep Caverns until
7you get a Rare Diamond to apply.
7A safe spot to do this is between the Diamond Reserve
7and the Obsidian Sanctuary (-20 27 70).
7Mobs don't spawn there.
7Wear armor enchanted with Growth 5
7(Enchanting Level 5), preferably Ender Armor
7while you're in The End or Mushroom Armor
7during the night.
7Applying Growth 5 costs 50 Levels each.
7If you still struggle, reforge your
7armor to Titanic.
7This needs Combat 15 and a completion
7of the 2 previous floors to enter.
7To efficiently grind this, you should
7get help from Party Finder/Friends.
7Use the best rod you can get
7your hands on (Chum Rod is a good option),
7enchant it and don't forget to use baits.
7You might also want to use Angler Armor.
7Do 3 Tier 1 Revenant Horror Bosses
7and claim the rewards by talking to Maddox.
7Doing this will bring you decently close
7to your 10th Minion Slot which will be
7useful for other goals. Craft all the
7Minions you get across. Remember that
7you can buy material from a few NPCs.
7Craft Leather, Iron, Gold and Diamond Armor
7and equip them all in one lobby.
7You will get decent progress towards this
7while going for other grinds. You will most
7likely have to kill some Enderman in The End
7to finish this. Don't forget to claim your
7bestiary rewards.
7Kill Cows in The Barn to unlock this
7and craft it using the materials you
7got along the way.
7Carrots and potatoes from killing
7Zombies in graveyard do count.
7This requires Catacombs Level 1 and
7a completion of the previous floor.
7You may need help from party finder
7or friends for this.
7You can unlock 17/17 Farming Collections,
76/11 Combat Collections, 6/6 Foraging Collections,
714/22 Mining Collections for a total of 43 collections.
7You will also get some Fishing Collections.
7You will need Heart of the Mountain 3
7for this (this can be done by doing
74 commissions a day for 3 days). In the
7Crystal Hollows you will need to find
7Mines of Divan and 4 different tools in there.
7You will need Heart of the Mountain 3
7for this (this can be done by doing
74 commissions a day for 3 days). Aim to
7use 10 or more Minions for this and give
7them the best fuel and storage you have
7access to. Collect in time!
7Get yourself a splash, equip a Bingo Pet
7and get the cake buff by eating the cakes
7on owocato's, xMeru's or prtl's island.
7If this doesn't finish it, get a Void Sword (200k) in the End
7and hold it while some Ender Armor and/or Equipment.
7You might want to go for Sugar Cane
7in your Garden, but you can also use
7the wheat in The Hub.
7Talk to Jamie in the Hub and
7claim the Rogue Sword from him.
7Right click it to gain +100 Speed.
7Or just wait for a splash.
7Get Enchanting Level 10 and play
7the first tier in the Experimentation Table.
7List of more than 12 talismans:
7Buy all 6 Talismans for 26k from the Adventurer in The Hub
7Collection Talismans:
7Night Vision Charm, Farming Talisman, Vaccine Talisman,
7Gravity Talisman, Talisman of Coins, Magnetic Talisman,
7Emerald Ring, Wood Affinity Talisman, Speed Talisman,
7Potion Affinity Talisman
7Other:
7Archaeologists Compass, Shiny Yellow Rock, King Talisman,
7Campfire Initiate Badge, Cat Talisman, Spider Talisman.
7Don't forget to take the 4 Bonus accessory bag slots from
7the Redstone Miner, he needs 1920 Redstone in total.
7To get the required Gold Medal you'll have
7to either trade in 4 Silver or 8 Bronze Medals
7with Anita. The crops recommended for this are:
7Wheat, Carrot, Potato, Cactus, and Mushroom.
7Buy a Dirt Bottle (100k) from Smithmonger in the Hub
7and reforge a weapon with it.
7Make sure to NOT shift-click it out
7of the menu after applying!
7For this you can kill Arachne in the Spider's Den,
7salvage the gear drops you get from that
7 and also gain Spider Essence from opening
7secret chests in dungeons.
7Claim your cake buff (visit skyerzz, xMeru or prtl)
7hold an Angler 4 or 5 rod and visit someone
7with a Sea Creature Chance beacon.
7Open chests in the Crystal Hollows (Heart of the Mountain III),
7do commissions in The Dwarven Mines,
7claim your daily powder from the Puzzler and
7from giving Fetchur the items he asks for.
7Fetchurs items are all listed in the Wiki.
7Try to do those while a '2x Powder' event is active.
7You will most likely get this from
7leveling up skills.
7Remember to actually put the money
7you get in the Bank :)
7Use a Chicken Head to get enough eggs
7to craft an Enchanted Egg (2.5k Chicken Collection).
7With your Enchanted Egg and 8 Move Jerry's,
7craft a Jerry pet.
7For this you either want to go for
7Wheat, Mushroom or Cobblestone.
7The first 2 options will require 75 pelts
7to get to t12. Use /warp trapper and SkyHanni's
7Trapper Features to help with that.
7You will get passive progress for this
7while going for other goals. If you want
7to specifically go for this, use a
7Cobblestone Generator on your island.
7You will passively get progress
7in this by just having a pet
7equipped all time. Even a
7Level 100 pet works for this.
7Use Enchanted Sugar that you get from
7killing pests in The Garden or from
7farming some Sugar Cane to brew
7Speed Potions (you will also need
7some nether warts for Awkward Potions first)
7Mine 50 Iron in the Gold Mine
7to unlock Iron Minions. Then buy
7Iron from the Mine Merchant in The Hub
7and Iron Forger in the Gold Mine and
7craft as many minions as you can.
7Give them the best fuel and storage you
7have access to and don't forget Auto Smelters.
7Remember to collect in time.
7To help with this, try to make bigger crafts
7by hand for Carpentry levels.
7Also do your daily experiments and make sure
7to have a pet active at all times
7(any pet works, even level 100).
7Save your coins from Meiser and ideally
7you get a score of 270+ in your run for
7High Score! You may need more coins than
7250k if you do drop rarer loot.
7Remember you can open chests at Croesus
7in the Dungeon Hub up to 48h after the run.
7Get yourself a splash, equip a Bingo Pet
7and get the cake buff by eating the cakes
7on owocato's, xMeru's or prtl's island.
7If this doesn't finish it, get a Void Sword (200k) in the End
7and hold it while some Ender Armor and/or Equipment.
7You will get passive progress for this
7while going for other goals. If you want
7to specifically go for this, use a
7Cobblestone Generator on your island.
7Unlock Skeleton Minions by killing skeletons you
7run into along your way. Then buy
7Bones from the Adventurer in The Hub
7and craft as many minions as you can.
7Give them the best fuel and storage you
7have access to.
7Remember to collect in time.
7You will most likely get this from
7leveling up skills.
7Remember to actually put the money
7you get in the Bank :)
7Wear armor enchanted with Growth 5
7(Enchanting Level 5), preferably Ender Armor
7while you're in The End or Mushroom Armor
7during the night.
7Applying Growth 5 costs 50 Levels each.
7If you still struggle, reforge your
7armor to Titanic.
7You will need Mining 12 for this as you
7need to enter the Dwarven Mines for this.
7Remember that Glacite Walkers take more
7damage from pickaxes.
7This requires Catacombs Level 1 and
7a completion of the previous floor.
7You may need help from party finder
7or friends for this.
7To get easy progress in this do
7contests like Wheat, Potato, Carrot
7or Mushroom as those are easy
7Bronze or Silver Medals to get.
7Optimal tool:
7Golden Axe with Efficiency 5
7Reforges: Double-Bit or Lush
7Get Haste 3 from a splash to instamine wood
7Forage in the Hub.
7Place as many minions as you can,
7give them a medium storage and the best fuel
7you can. Collect them in time.

24.description: 7Get Bronze or higher in a contest
guide: 7For this you will need Farming 10.
7Your best options for this will probably be
7Wheat/Potato/Carrot in the Garden or Mushroom
7if you use an Efficiency 5 Silk Touch Gold Axe
7in the Desert.
7Buy a Dirt Bottle (100k) from the Smithmonger
7in the Hub and reforge a weapon with it.
74Make sure to NOT shift-click it out
74of the menu after applying!
7You will get some progress for this
7by working on other goals.
7The easiest to go for are:
7Mushroom, Oak Wood, Bone,
7Sand, Wheat, Iron and Seeds.
7Reforge your Void Sword to Sharp
7at the Blacksmith in the Hub,
7or enchant any weapon with Critical 5
7(costs 50 Levels).
7For this you will need Combat 15 and
7completion of the previous floor.
7Going for this with your friends is
7probably the best option or you
7could use party finder.
7Get the common Rock from mining
72.5k Ores and hand it to Kat in The Hub
7(takes a day and 100k coins) or mine
75k more Ores to get the uncommon Rock.
7Remember to equip it!
7Craft Leather, Iron, Gold, Diamond, Mushroom
7and Leaflet Armor. Grind Glacite Armor
7for the goal I've got Chills!
7and equip them all in one lobby.
7Hit 10 Endermen in The End
7so they follow you, then kill them
7all as quickly as you can.
7You most likely want to use Ender Armor
7and a Void Sword for this.
7Do 3 Tier 1 Revenant Horror Bosses
7and claim the rewards by talking to Maddox.
7nNo eggs:r
7Bingo, Endermen, Grandma Wolf, Armadillo,
7Squid, Guardian, Bee, Dolphin, Reindeer,
7Rock, Tarantula, Owl and Zoo
7nEggs:r
7Jerry, Silverfish, Pig, Rabbit, Endermite and Bat
7If you do eggs you will need 2.5k Chicken Collection
7and you'll want a Chicken Minion that can create more
7Enchanted Eggs for you once you put your first one in.
7Once you acquire a Void Sword and a decent
7armor like Ender or Glacite this should be
7fairly easy to do. You might get a little
7progress in this from doing the Slayer Goal.
